---
description: Contract rules for protobuf/OpenAPI packages
globs:
  - "libs/contracts/**"
  - "**/*.proto"
---

- Packages are versioned: `voxmesh.<domain>.v1`. Breaking changes require a new package version
  or an explicit, documented migration strategy — `buf breaking` enforces this in CI.
- Never reuse or renumber existing field numbers; reserve removed fields.
- Transcript segments are revisioned records: stable prefix + mutable suffix + revision number +
  final flag. Partials replace the mutable revision of the same segment; they are never emitted
  as independent final records.
- Provider-specific (Teams/Meet/Zoom) schemas stay inside their adapters — never add
  provider-shaped fields to shared contracts.
- Run `npx @bufbuild/buf lint libs/contracts/proto` before committing contract changes.
